      "text": "Design a notification system",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Design a notification system",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Kz5tO4ts9D5KXKyy8lOPG",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 222.65467834472656,
      "y": 230.05865478515625,
      "width": 623.2595825195312,
      "height": 775,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bAR",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1574108082,
      "version": 577,
      "versionNonce": 1343023154,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782619459494,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Questions :\n1. service t service communication?\nyes\n\n2. imp features?\nsend push notification, sms and email?\nyes\n\n3. scale\n10 m push notifications \n1 m emails \n5 m sms\nper day\n\n4. API or event interface?\nboth\n\n5. templates for notifications\nmay be, if time permits\n\n6. near real time?\nyes\n\n\nFunctional req:\n- send notifications via send push notification, sms and email\n- users can opt out\n- users can select channels they want to be notified ( optional)\n- and select rate at which they want notification ( optional)\n- using 3rd party like APN, FCM, email and sms service\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Questions :\n1. service t service communication?\nyes\n\n2. imp features?\nsend push notification, sms and email?\nyes\n\n3. scale\n10 m push notifications \n1 m emails \n5 m sms\nper day\n\n4. API or event interface?\nboth\n\n5. templates for notifications\nmay be, if time permits\n\n6. near real time?\nyes\n\n\nFunctional req:\n- send notifications via send push notification, sms and email\n- users can opt out\n- users can select channels they want to be notified ( optional)\n- and select rate at which they want notification ( optional)\n- using 3rd party like APN, FCM, email and sms service\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "hRXD8xda7Yps8UymhfR1L",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 222,
      "y": 1021.5,
      "width": 520.9396362304688,
      "height": 750,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bAS",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 400865646,
      "version": 476,
      "versionNonce": 834300910,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782619459494,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "NFR:\n- Availability : 99.9 ( 8.8 hours of downtime per year)\n- Durability : 6 9s\n- Scalable\n- FLexible\n- Near real time delivery\n\n\nback of the envelope calculations\n\nTraffic:\n10m push notifications per day\n10m / 100,000 ( 84600 second)\n= 10^7 / 10^5\n= 100 rps\nsms\n= 50 rps\nemails\n= 10 rps\n\nstorage \n= 10m + 1 + 5\n= 16m per day\n= 10kb * 16 m\n= 160 kb * 10^6\n= 160 GB per day\n= 160 * 365 GB per year\n= 160 * 400 gb\n= 64 * 10 * 100\n= 64 TB per year",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "NFR:\n- Availability : 99.9 ( 8.8 hours of downtime per year)\n- Durability : 6 9s\n- Scalable\n- FLexible\n- Near real time delivery\n\n\nback of the envelope calculations\n\nTraffic:\n10m push notifications per day\n10m / 100,000 ( 84600 second)\n= 10^7 / 10^5\n= 100 rps\nsms\n= 50 rps\nemails\n= 10 rps\n\nstorage \n= 10m + 1 + 5\n= 16m per day\n= 10kb * 16 m\n= 160 kb * 10^6\n= 160 GB per day\n= 160 * 365 GB per year\n= 160 * 400 gb\n= 64 * 10 * 100\n= 64 TB per year",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
