      "versionNonce": 1723820590,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782619459494,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Reliability\n- prevent duplication of notifications : \nNS send idempotency key which adapter reads and processes\n- adapters have retry mechanism if it fails\n\nTemplate\n\nAddiotional things :\nrate limiting\npririty of notifications\nretry mechanism : use DLQ along with SNS/ SQS\n\nMonitors\nSLA\navailability\nlatency\ndurability\n\nbuisness metrics\nDAU\nend to end time\nclick rate cvr\nopen rate cvr\nnotifications sent in a time period\nfailure rate",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Reliability\n- prevent duplication of notifications : \nNS send idempotency key which adapter reads and processes\n- adapters have retry mechanism if it fails\n\nTemplate\n\nAddiotional things :\nrate limiting\npririty of notifications\nretry mechanism : use DLQ along with SNS/ SQS\n\nMonitors\nSLA\navailability\nlatency\ndurability\n\nbuisness metrics\nDAU\nend to end time\nclick rate cvr\nopen rate cvr\nnotifications sent in a time period\nfailure rate",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
