      "text": "Design chat system",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Design chat system",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "2XnL4lvgQu8IAHiiMUazV",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 231.01193237304688,
      "y": 204.66769409179688,
      "width": 548.7595825195312,
      "height": 625,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bE2",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 78169138,
      "version": 288,
      "versionNonce": 543636530,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782619790507,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Questions:\n\n1. Design chat system similar to whatsapp, fb messager?\nyes, whatsapp\n\n2. 1:1 chat or group or both\nboth\n\n3. online, offline indication\nyes\n\n4. support attachment\nmaybe\n\n5. scale\n500m DAU\n\n6.any limits to messages\nno\n\n7. store messages\nforeever\n\n8. group limit\n200",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Questions:\n\n1. Design chat system similar to whatsapp, fb messager?\nyes, whatsapp\n\n2. 1:1 chat or group or both\nboth\n\n3. online, offline indication\nyes\n\n4. support attachment\nmaybe\n\n5. scale\n500m DAU\n\n6.any limits to messages\nno\n\n7. store messages\nforeever\n\n8. group limit\n200",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "rjlpnRN3xvrpdVyW57N2u",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 231.4752197265625,
      "y": 863.0493774414062,
      "width": 545.5596923828125,
      "height": 275,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bE3",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1080514482,
      "version": 252,
      "versionNonce": 783548594,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782619878065,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Functional req:\n1. User should be able to send message to another user\n2. user send message in group\n3. online, offline status\n\nNon functional req:\n1. Availability : 99.9\n2. Scalable\n3. low latency\n4. Consistent ( messages appear in order)\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Functional req:\n1. User should be able to send message to another user\n2. user send message in group\n3. online, offline status\n\nNon functional req:\n1. Availability : 99.9\n2. Scalable\n3. low latency\n4. Consistent ( messages appear in order)\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "DPt92E-7cyFqTXn_FJAYj",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 231.04244995117188,
      "y": 1151.9313354492188,
      "width": 338.259765625,
      "height": 425,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bE4",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 615316530,
      "version": 260,
      "versionNonce": 864162610,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782620200152,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Back of the enevelope calculations\n\n500 m DAU\n40 message a day\n20000 message a day\n100 bytes : unicode \n\n20b * 100 b\n= 2b * 1kb\n= 2 * 10^9 kb\n= 2 tb\n\n5 years of storage\n= 2 * 365 * 5 tb\n= 3560 tb\n= 3.6 pb\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Back of the enevelope calculations\n\n500 m DAU\n40 message a day\n20000 message a day\n100 bytes : unicode \n\n20b * 100 b\n= 2b * 1kb\n= 2 * 10^9 kb\n= 2 tb\n\n5 years of storage\n= 2 * 365 * 5 tb\n= 3560 tb\n= 3.6 pb\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
