      "text": "APIs:\n\nGET /api/v1/ws\nAuthorization: Bearer JWT\nServer:\n101 Switching Protocols\n\nclinet send over WS\ntype : SEND_MESSAGE\nserver : MESSAGE_ACCEPTED\n\nserver pushes type NEW_MESSAGE to anther user\nanother user type READ_RECEIPT\nif another user offline. then after coming back online \nGET /v1/conversations/{id}/messages?afterSequence=451&limit=100\n\n\n\nPOST /api/v1/presence/\nGET /api/v1/presence/\nPOST /api/v1/groups : create group\nPUT, PATCH /api/v1/users\n\ntype of messages for WS:\nCONNECT\nDISCONNECT\nSEND_MESSAGE\nNEW_MESSAGE\nMESSAGE_ACCEPTED\nREAD_RECEIPT\nMESSAGE_READ\nTYPING\nSTOP_TYPING\nONLINE\nOFFLINE\nPING\nPONG\n\nevents :\nmessage-sent.v1\nmessage-delivered.v1\nmessage-read.v1\nuser-presence-connected.v1",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "APIs:\n\nGET /api/v1/ws\nAuthorization: Bearer JWT\nServer:\n101 Switching Protocols\n\nclinet send over WS\ntype : SEND_MESSAGE\nserver : MESSAGE_ACCEPTED\n\nserver pushes type NEW_MESSAGE to anther user\nanother user type READ_RECEIPT\nif another user offline. then after coming back online \nGET /v1/conversations/{id}/messages?afterSequence=451&limit=100\n\n\n\nPOST /api/v1/presence/\nGET /api/v1/presence/\nPOST /api/v1/groups : create group\nPUT, PATCH /api/v1/users\n\ntype of messages for WS:\nCONNECT\nDISCONNECT\nSEND_MESSAGE\nNEW_MESSAGE\nMESSAGE_ACCEPTED\nREAD_RECEIPT\nMESSAGE_READ\nTYPING\nSTOP_TYPING\nONLINE\nOFFLINE\nPING\nPONG\n\nevents :\nmessage-sent.v1\nmessage-delivered.v1\nmessage-read.v1\nuser-presence-connected.v1",
